To use the simple.py, 

./simple.py => This generates a manifest.xml file using the MASTER, VM1,
VM2, etc. ip-adddresses listed inside the simple.py script.
One shall edit the MASTER, VM1, etc. to suit their VMs in order to use
the manifest.xml in an expanded mode.

Options:
-l - Generates a manifest.xml to be used in collapsed mode
-m - Generates a manifest.xml with multi-dts-router option turned on.

